Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, the quizzes{quiz lab} start at one...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not so sure about the shogi tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.44,0:01:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But I definitely need to check out the cooking contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.83,0:01:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally tomorrow!
