Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:23.52,Default,,0,0,10,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.52,0:02:26.37,Default,,0,0,10,,Hey! You're up early, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:27.92,Default,,0,0,10,,You've got the culture fair today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.92,0:02:28.74,Default,,0,0,10,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:30.46,Default,,0,0,10,,I get the feeling you might run into a few issues.{from context this sounds like a prediction?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you get {\i1}that{\i0} feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Classics Club tradition to run into trouble during the culture fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I could do without a tradition that's gonna cause me trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.74,0:02:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The least you could do is give me a good-luck charm, Ms. Senio—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There. You can have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I supposed to say thanks?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:02:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, it's out of ink and the tip is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't recall becoming a trash can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.21,0:03:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drop by if I feel bored enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the culture fair, Houtarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.72,0:03:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It would seem so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You never change, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And you still seem to be enjoying yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The culture fair is the one great constant of all club traditions!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.71,0:03:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, isn't that Mayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She's probably dressed up for the Manga Lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,From the looks of it, they're also scheduled to work at the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have something on your mind as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the Handicraft Club, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me say hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.93,0:03:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Those clothes look good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And who are you cosp—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't use words like that in front of normal people.{lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.98,0:04:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, who are you dressed as?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Frol.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Frol? Frolbericheri Frol?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.64,0:04:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put on gloves later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.23,0:04:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's in your bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This and that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So are you gonna be at the Manga Lab the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I ended up having to work at the counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.61,0:04:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, of all days!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do anything about the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it! The culture fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a lot about it, but this exceeds all my expectations!{from the stories}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A little {\i1}too{\i0} lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're done?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's get this done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll part with you here for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.46,0:05:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Going sewing?{The Handicrafts club?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.62,0:05:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.89,0:05:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's awfully quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Get over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep dwelling on that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll get Chitanda fixated on it as well as Satoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
