Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Oreki, Mayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give it our best shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Though will that even help in this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.56,0:06:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no guarantee it'll work out even if we try our hardest,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but I {\i1}can{\i0} guarantee it won't work out unless we put effort into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I guess I {\i1}will{\i0} buy some!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not why I said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm the one who ordered them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How many did we plan on originally?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And how many have we got now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Two hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Galaxy!{w}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, my Saturn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Fukube.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. We haven't started yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault for not double-checking our order with the printing company.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone makes mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're saying that in those clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't take all the blame upon yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.69,0:07:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're saying {\i0}that{\i1} in those clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,As club president, it was my responsibility to check it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I just handed over the manuscript and didn't pay any further attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our collective responsibility as members of the Classics Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:07:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stop saying stuff like that in those clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no time until the opening ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Does anyone have any idea how we could sell most of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How much does one cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,200 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.53,0:08:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is the Classics Club isn't well-known
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're cursed with a bad location.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So first off we need to get the word out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and find a better place from which to sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we going to set up a new stall?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been trying to think of ways to lure customers here all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This will turn the tables on them, Oreki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't really go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But would we get permission to do that at this point{当日}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in the council, so tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd have to be a special exception,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.96,0:09:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so you'd need to ask the Student Council president
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.90,0:09:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,or our General Affairs president directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's handling General Affairs at the moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You could at least look at the guide, Houtarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:13.69,signs,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.25\blur0.55\an5\fs20\fnArial Rounded MT\c&H2A2B2E&\b1\pos(413,317)\frz331.3\frx34\fry8}President:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:13.69,signs,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.25\blur0.55\an5\fs20\fnArial Rounded MT\c&H2A2B2E&\b1\pos(515,364)\frz328.9\frx34\fry6}Tanabe Jirou
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,First time I've seen that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I hoped you'd notice my little trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think? Subtle, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at the end of the club list, and here's the Classics Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I pulled a few strings to get it in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This booklet was edited by those of us at General Affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,More like you're abusing your authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to talk to the president, go to the meeting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you ask him for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not really the diplomatic type.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitanda, you should go talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be there to offer moral support.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it. Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't seem all that enthusiastic about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But more importantly, I'll promote our club myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why you're dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a special move!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have a new idea we can use?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We should enter the culture fair's events and contests under the club's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.81,0:10:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If we play our cards right, our club could gain fame and fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're just in this to have fun, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a wonderful idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.69,0:10:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Fukube!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait a moment.{hou overlap}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good idea. Let's make that our main approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.49,0:10:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitanda should negotiate for a better selling spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoshi's in charge of promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stick to that for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But... what about you, Oreki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...hold the fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, someone {\i1}does{\i0} have to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.93,0:11:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The opening ceremony's about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,let's stick to the plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and sell as many as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The goal is to sell all 200 copies of {\i1}Hyouka{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey-hey-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...Ho.
