Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:37.56,signs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\fs34\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\b0\c&H4B6F64&\pos(630,141)}General Council Office
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. I'm looking for the president of the General Council, Tanabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give the Classics Club more stall space!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Global act! Global act!{acting? action? idk}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Classics Club's president, Chitanda Eru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.78,0:15:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have a huge favor to ask of to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give the Classics Club more stall space!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just approve a request out of nowhere like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not possible? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.13,0:15:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just our general policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me your particular circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wasn't Fukube supposed to be around for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So I prepared to accelerate, and shouted—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait wait wait, that's not gonna cut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you senile or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But it works!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No it doesn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's definitely a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.11,0:16:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I really would like to help,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,but all clubs could cite such circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't make an exception just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not possible after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanted to ask other clubs to offer your anthology for sale,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that'd be perfectly fine with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a great idea! We'll definitely consider it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
