Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ibara.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawachi, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you even brought a sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.02,0:17:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, though it's just a plastic replica.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've done the shoes too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So she dressed up after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She was totally against it to start with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Should've just listened to Kawachi from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't put it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.17,0:18:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Yuasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, President.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.97,0:18:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have to spend much on your outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.54,0:18:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have your receipt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.31,0:18:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But more importantly, President,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,could we—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.45,0:18:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to bring myself to ask if we can sell {\i1}Hyouka{\i0} here.
