Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who're you dressed as?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.59,0:18:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? Frol.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, from "They Were Eleven"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of that one.
