Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A real classic, in my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you lend it to me next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:18:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
