Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hooray for shopkeeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, how many confirmed sales do we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.77,0:19:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Given the situation, the club members buy two each.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,With those, and the ones for our advisor and the archive,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that's twelve right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that counts as selling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, have you seen my apple juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.43,0:20:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, I'd barely even taken a sip.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:20:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, I'm sleepy.{you and me both, houtarou}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.34,0:21:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh! A punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.37,0:21:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This guy's a punk, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, whatcha doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.30,0:21:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothin— I mean, we're selling an anthology.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.13,0:21:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All of those?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.74,0:21:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.93,0:21:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A customer? Gotta act friendly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be 200 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.92,0:21:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not smiling at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.11,0:21:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I take a look at that for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.81,0:21:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.02,0:21:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the Fashion Lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.89,0:21:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doing a fashion show,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:21:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but I forgot to bring something to use as a formal pocket accessory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.99,0:22:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.95,0:22:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.54,0:22:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously? Can I really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.44,0:22:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's basically trash anyway, so feel free.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.22,0:22:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the winning number for our show,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:12.64,signs,,0,0,0,,{\fscx50\blur0.6\an5\c&H171C18&\fnSwagger\frz11.81\frx4\fry34\pos(606,497)}Fashion Lab
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.64,0:22:12.76,signs,,0,0,0,,{\fscx70\blur0.6\an5\c&H333D31&\fnSwagger\frz6.948\frx358\fry16\pos(572,512)\iclip(m 508 535 l 514 526 522 514 534 498 637 484 630 546)}Fashion Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:12.76,signs,,0,0,0,,{\fscx70\blur0.6\an5\c&H171C18&\fnSwagger\frz6.948\frx358\fry16\pos(572,512)\clip(m 508 535 l 514 526 522 514 534 498 637 484 630 546)}Fashion Lab
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.76,0:22:13.93,signs,,0,0,0,,{\fscx75\blur0.6\an5\c&H333D31&\fnSwagger\frz6.948\pos(550,517)\frx0\fry6\iclip(m 504 544 l 513 532 524 519 538 501 634 495 622 547)}Fashion Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:13.93,signs,,0,0,0,,{\fscx75\blur0.6\an5\c&H171C18&\fnSwagger\frz6.948\pos(550,517)\frx0\fry6\clip(m 504 544 l 513 532 524 519 538 501 634 495 622 547)}Fashion Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,so if you bring that to our changing room,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.08,0:22:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll get you into the spotlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.28,0:22:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This would be more Satoshi's style.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.91,0:22:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Actually, I think his style is a little beyond me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.34,0:22:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So much for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.88,0:22:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But at least I managed to sell a copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.35,0:22:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, I did it again!{chitney spears}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.50,0:22:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:22:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.98,0:22:57.98,signs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.7\fscy95\an9\fnSwagger\pos(734,161)\c&H27383B&\b1}Taking keepsake \N\N\N\N\Nphotos!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.98,0:22:57.98,signs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.7\fs30\fnappo paint\b1\pos(640,576)\c&H1A262E&}Photography Club
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.45,0:23:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.16,0:23:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, this won't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.78,0:23:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't do my job if I keep getting sidetracked by anything interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.41,0:23:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Occult Seekers! We're the Occult Seekers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.09,0:23:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna watch UFOs together?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.84,0:23:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We have ghost photos as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.33,0:23:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The Enterprise is on exhibit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.07,0:23:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The launching ceremony starts soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Global act!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.56,0:23:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Want a charm?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.98,0:23:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}Hasn't anyone invented glasses that only let you look straight ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.00,0:24:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.22,0:24:18.95,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}The situation is unscientific
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.89,0:24:22.93,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)}A montage of emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.93,0:24:25.48,ED,,0,0,0,,Who's calling who?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.48,0:24:29.69,ED,,0,0,0,,You look away when our eyes are about to meet
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.69,0:24:31.52,ED top,,0,0,0,,I can feel it
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.52,0:24:33.78,ED,,0,0,0,,Am I just imagining things? It's so cold of you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.78,0:24:39.34,ED,,0,0,0,,It takes talent to read minds
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.34,0:24:40.50,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}You know
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.20,0:24:41.83,ED top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You know
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.29,0:24:43.25,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wanna know
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.03,0:24:44.89,ED top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.29,0:24:54.06,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}I'll fix the fire of youth in your heart while I can
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.10,0:24:55.84,ED top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}If we can do it today why leave it for tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.84,0:25:01.43,ED,,0,0,0,,I want to solve your mystery
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.43,0:25:06.72,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Look for the back of the boy, burdened with secrets
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.14,0:25:07.82,ED top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even today
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.10,0:25:12.39,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)}You are a fantasy and I'm drawn to you
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.39,0:25:16.58,ED,,0,0,0,,This growing curiosity
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.58,0:25:19.37,ED,,0,0,0,,There's no twist in the story
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.37,0:25:20.80,ED,,0,0,0,,I can't stop thinking about it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.80,0:25:23.81,ED,,0,0,0,,It's so interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.81,0:25:26.33,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,350)}But why?
